<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Mba tahio Jeso o! FFPM328</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Mba tahio, Jeso ô !
 Hira, hatakay sy teny ;
 Mba tarihonao ny fo
 Hanarahanay ireny ;
 Hianao no Tompon'aina,
 Sady mendri-koderaina.

[V2]
 Izahay mpanomponao
 Hody ao an-tokantrano,
 Faly manana Anao,
 Ka vimbino sy tantano ;
 Aza avela ho irery,
 Izahay, fandrao ho very.

[V3]
 Saotra no atolotray,
 Raha mbola atý an-tany ;
 Ao an-danitra indray
 Dia dera tsy ho lany
 No hatao sy hohiraina
 Ho Anao ry Tompon'aina.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>328</hymn_number>
<author>J. R. Ahle</author>
</song>